| `lowrank_expert_residual` | `x_hat = Σ_r β_r u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i} b_{e,i} + Σ_j γ_j c_j` | candidate | trunk + expert 子库 + 全局 residual 补偿都落在静态向量库上 | 扩展兼容 |
